{"_id":"C7aHeFis3ojINgAc","name":"Stage II Abomination \"Mutant\"","permission":{"default":0,"q8HmJQOf882klbgH":3},"type":"creature","data":{"header":{"health":{"value":0,"label":"Health","max":0}},"attributes":{"speed":{"value":2,"label":"Speed"},"armorrating":{"value":0,"label":"Number","max":10}},"general":{"mobility":{"value":"-","label":"Mobility"},"observation":{"value":"-","label":"Observation"},"comment":{"value":"","label":"Text"},"special":{"value":"","label":"Text"},"acidSplash":{"value":"-","label":"Acid Splash"}},"notes":"<p>TRAITS: Aggressive Dementia, Cerebral Dysmorphia</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Painful cellular mutations ravage the Abomination&rsquo;s body, causing them to take on an aggressive posture.</p>\n<p>The subject&rsquo;s limbs distend and become pliable, allowing them to contort into strange positions. The brain and skull continue to elongate and the subject takes on a feral appearance and attitude.</p>\n<p>Strength, speed, and agility are all heightened. Only a rudimentary knowledge of their former self remains, but they are still aware enough to use basic tools and weapons.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>EFFECTS:</p>\n<p>The subject gets Speed 2, i.e. it gets to act twice per Round.</p>\n<p><strong>STRENGTH </strong>increases by 3 (and Health along with it).</p>\n<p><strong>AGILITY </strong>is increased by 1, while <strong>EMPATHY </strong>is reduced to 1.</p>\n<p><strong>EMPATHY</strong>-based skills cannot be used.</p>\n<p>Firearms and other technological items cannot be used.</p>\n<p>The subject becomes immune to <strong>MANIPULATION </strong>.</p>\n<p>At this point, the subject becomes aggressive and attacks other humans on sight.</p>\n<p>An infected PC can play out one such attack, then the subject turns into an NPC controlled by the GM.</p>\n<p>Within one Shift, the subject advances to Stage III.</p>","rTables":"None"},"sort":100001,"flags":{},"token":{"flags":{},"name":"Stage II Abomination \"Mutant\"","displayName":20,"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","tint":null,"width":1,"height":1,"scale":1,"lockRotation":false,"rotation":0,"vision":true,"dimSight":0,"brightSight":0,"dimLight":0,"brightLight":0,"sightAngle":360,"lightAngle":360,"lightAlpha":1,"lightAnimation":{"speed":5,"intensity":5},"actorId":"C7aHeFis3ojINgAc","actorLink":false,"disposition":-1,"displayBars":20,"bar1":{"attribute":"header.health"},"bar2":{},"randomImg":false},"items":[],"effects":[]}
{"_id":"MsDslIE6Yv7WHrmT","name":"Stage IV Abomination \"Beluga-Head\"","permission":{"default":0,"q8HmJQOf882klbgH":3},"type":"creature","data":{"header":{"health":{"value":10,"label":"Health","max":10}},"attributes":{"speed":{"value":2,"label":"Speed"},"armorrating":{"value":6,"label":"Number","max":10}},"general":{"mobility":{"value":"5","label":"Mobility"},"observation":{"value":"3","label":"Observation"},"comment":{"value":"","label":"Text"},"special":{"value":"Armor rating 6 (3 against fire damage)","label":"Text"},"acidSplash":{"value":"-","label":"Acid Splash"}},"notes":"<p>TRAITS:</p>\n<p>Complete Cellular Metamorphosis</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The subject&rsquo;s gelatinous cowl grows opaque and solidifies as their eyes grow dark and shift to the sides of their bulbous head.</p>\n<p>Their skin turns a translucent mottled gray and their features grow similar in appearance to a Xenomorph XX121, albeit with a much shorter head, more prominent eyes and elongated arms.</p>\n<p>The subject moves about on all fours like an ape and no longer retains any human characteristics.</p>\n<p>While not as powerful or intelligent as a Xenomorph XX121, the Beluga-Head is a force to be reckoned with.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>EFFECTS:</p>\n<p>As Stage III, with <strong>STRENGTH </strong>increasing by yet another 2 (and Health along with it).</p>\n<p>Cowl now gives a natural Armor Rating of 6.</p>","rTables":"Abomination Attacks (Stage III and IV)"},"sort":100001,"flags":{},"img":"worlds/alien-cotg/creatures/abomination-stage-iv-belugahead.jpg","token":{"flags":{},"name":"Stage IV Abomination \"Beluga-Head\"","displayName":20,"img":"worlds/alien-cotg/creatures/abomination-stage-iv-belugahead.jpg","tint":null,"width":1,"height":1,"scale":1,"lockRotation":false,"rotation":0,"vision":true,"dimSight":0,"brightSight":0,"dimLight":0,"brightLight":0,"sightAngle":360,"lightAngle":360,"lightAlpha":1,"lightAnimation":{"speed":5,"intensity":5},"actorId":"MsDslIE6Yv7WHrmT","actorLink":false,"disposition":-1,"displayBars":20,"bar1":{"attribute":"header.health"},"bar2":{},"randomImg":false},"items":[],"effects":[]}
{"_id":"ipN72INSjrMUTodF","name":"Stage III Abomination \"Revenant\"","permission":{"default":0,"q8HmJQOf882klbgH":3},"type":"creature","data":{"header":{"health":{"value":8,"label":"Health","max":8}},"attributes":{"speed":{"value":2,"label":"Speed"},"armorrating":{"value":3,"label":"Number","max":10}},"general":{"mobility":{"value":"5","label":"Mobility"},"observation":{"value":"3","label":"Observation"},"comment":{"value":"","label":"Text"},"special":{"value":"Armor rating 3 (nothing against fire)\n\nSTRENGTH increases by a further 2 (and Health along with it).\n\nAGILITY is increased by 1 more.\n\nWITS is reduced to 1. No skills based on WITS except OBSERVATION can be used.\n\nImmune to MANIPULATION and panic.\n\nCowl gives a natural Armor Rating of 3.\n\nThe subject is now handled as a full Xenomorph and gets its own table for signature attacks (see next page).\n\nWithin four Shifts, the subject advances to Stage IV.","label":"Text"},"acidSplash":{"value":"-","label":"Acid Splash"}},"notes":"<p>TRAITS:</p>\n<p>Instinctual Aggression, Advanced Dementia</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The subject&rsquo;s body is in an advanced state of DNA recoding. A translucent, gelatinous cowl has grown over most of their head, revealing a sunken and hideous caricature of their former visage beneath.</p>\n<p>As the structure of the subject&rsquo;s original features dis- solves into the acidic gelatin, their skull becomes more pronounced.</p>\n<p>Eventually, any semblance of human origin recedes and becomes barely visible within the cowl. The subject&rsquo;s feet each splay into three thick toes, their arms elongate like a primate&rsquo;s, and they sprint using their knuckles to propel themselves.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>EFFECTS:</p>\n<p><strong>STRENGTH </strong>increases by a further 2 (and Health along with it).</p>\n<p><strong>AGILITY </strong>is increased by 1 more.</p>\n<p><strong>WITS </strong>is reduced to 1. No skills based on WITS except <strong>OBSERVATION </strong>can be used.</p>\n<p>Immune to <strong>MANIPULATION </strong>and panic.</p>\n<p>Cowl gives a natural Armor Rating of 3.</p>\n<p>The subject is now handled as a full Xenomorph and gets its own table for signature attacks (see next page).</p>\n<p>Within four Shifts, the subject advances to Stage IV.</p>","rTables":"Abomination Attacks (Stage III and IV)"},"sort":100001,"flags":{},"img":"worlds/alien-cotg/creatures/abomination-stage-iii-revenant.png","token":{"flags":{},"name":"Stage III Abomination \"Revenant\"","displayName":20,"img":"worlds/alien-cotg/creatures/abomination-stage-iii-revenant.png","tint":null,"width":1,"height":1,"scale":1,"lockRotation":false,"rotation":0,"vision":true,"dimSight":0,"brightSight":0,"dimLight":0,"brightLight":0,"sightAngle":360,"lightAngle":360,"lightAlpha":1,"lightAnimation":{"speed":5,"intensity":5},"actorId":"ipN72INSjrMUTodF","actorLink":false,"disposition":-1,"displayBars":20,"bar1":{"attribute":"header.health"},"bar2":{},"randomImg":false},"items":[],"effects":[]}
{"_id":"woXg39XEOboyYgte","name":"Stage I Abomination \"Infected\"","permission":{"default":0,"q8HmJQOf882klbgH":3},"type":"creature","data":{"header":{"health":{"value":0,"label":"Health","max":0}},"attributes":{"speed":{"value":0,"label":"Speed"},"armorrating":{"value":0,"label":"Number","max":10}},"general":{"mobility":{"value":"-","label":"Mobility"},"observation":{"value":"-","label":"Observation"},"comment":{"value":"","label":"Text"},"special":{"value":"","label":"Text"},"acidSplash":{"value":"-","label":"Acid Splash"}},"notes":"<p>TRAITS: Anger, Confusion, Acidosis</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Changes begin with the onset of rapid skin mottling that starts in the subject&rsquo;s extremities and moves inward towards the core body.</p>\n<p>Eventually the subject&rsquo;s skull begins to soften and elongate as their brain grows and is rewired.</p>\n<p>By the end of this stage, the process becomes excruciating and the subject lashes out.</p>\n<p>As acidosis takes effect, the subject&rsquo;s pH levels shift significantly.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>INFECTION:</p>\n<p>Exposure to the 26 Draconis Strain is normally handled as a disease with Virulence 6.</p>\n<p>If the Sickness Roll fails, the patient enters Stage I. For the purposes of this Cinematic scenario, you as GM are allowed skip the roll and simply decide if a PC is infected, for maximum dramatic effect.</p>\n<p>Within one Shift, the patient starts to exhibit the first symptoms, which causes their <strong>STRESS LEVEL</strong> to increase by one. Within another Shift, the patient typically advances to Stage II.</p>","rTables":"None"},"sort":100001,"flags":{},"token":{"flags":{},"name":"Stage I Abomination \"Infected\"","displayName":20,"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","tint":null,"width":1,"height":1,"scale":1,"lockRotation":false,"rotation":0,"vision":true,"dimSight":0,"brightSight":0,"dimLight":0,"brightLight":0,"sightAngle":360,"lightAngle":360,"lightAlpha":1,"lightAnimation":{"speed":5,"intensity":5},"actorId":"woXg39XEOboyYgte","actorLink":false,"disposition":-1,"displayBars":20,"bar1":{"attribute":"header.health"},"bar2":{},"randomImg":false},"items":[],"effects":[]}
